 \"Yulo scripted history in theParis Olympics 2024by becoming only the second-ever athlete from the Philippines to win an Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999997230361642, \"rank\": 2.7482011770726406e-07, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He became the first to ever win two gold medals.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While his legendary win made headlines in the country, Yulo is now in the news for different reasons.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8904675824643568e-19, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a TikTok video which shows him sitting next to girlfriend Chloe Anjeleigh San Jose, the Olympic gymnast accused his mother of draining his bank account.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.363825413516503e-26, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.7353203409386434, \"rank\": 0.3597217268535228, \"text\": \"Chloe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\", \"score\": 0.9927068052251979, \"rank\": 0.007330548545434048, \"text\": \"San Jose\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Jose_Earthquakes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Apart from the incentives, my mom also had access to my bank account and my monthly allowances for gymnastics.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I finally got control of that bank account, I found out she had been draining it.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have the bank statements showing the withdrawals she made,\\\" Yulo said in Filipino, according to news website Inquirer.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOlympicgold winner said he never received the six-figure incentive he was supposed to receive from an earlier tournament, and asked where the money went.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not have known that she had received them if I had not looked for them myself.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never received those incentives, and I never asked them for it.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have given up on it; it's no longer mine,\\\" Yulo said.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carols Yulo's mother, Angelica Yulo, said she transferred the money out of her son's account for safekeeping.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8904675824643568e-19, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angelica_Pickles\", \"score\": 0.9998909472109992, \"rank\": 0.00010395164658607027, \"text\": \"Angelica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angelica_Pickles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angelica_Pickles\"}, {\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8904675824643568e-19, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with Bombo Radyo earlier this week, she said: \\\"it was given to me.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bombo_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999614812977775, \"rank\": 0.0002317766888172581, \"text\": \"Bombo\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bombo_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bombo_railway_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a mother, I felt that my child might run out of money in the future.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, what I did was deposit it under my name at BPI here in Vito Cruz.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1778, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bank_of_the_Philippine_Islands\", \"score\": 0.9999992984369516, \"rank\": 7.014808841529872e-07, \"text\": \"BPI\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bank_of_the_Philippine_Islands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bank_of_the_Philippine_Islands\"}, {\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Cruz_station_(LRT)\", \"score\": 0.554455301202472, \"rank\": 0.8035714285715181, \"text\": \"Vito Cruz\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Cruz_station_(LRT)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vito_Cruz_station_(LRT)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, I held on to it and turned it into a bond for a credit card.\\\"\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo, however, has accused his mother of lying about how much incentive money he actually received.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also said the issue is not the money, but the principle.\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The issue here is not on how little or big the amount was that she handled, but her hiding and handling it without my consent, which I am pointing out to her,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Angelica Yulo claims that her son's girlfriend is the root cause of their rift.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2202, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angelica_Pickles\", \"score\": 0.9998909472109992, \"rank\": 0.00010395164658607027, \"text\": \"Angelica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angelica_Pickles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angelica_Pickles\"}, {\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8904675824643568e-19, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo, 24, also addressed the girlfriend issue.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said his mother has never liked Chloe.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She said our misunderstanding started because of Chloe.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's true.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever since the beginning, she did not like Chloe, even though she had not met or seen her in person.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2492, \"end\": 2497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.7353203409386434, \"rank\": 0.3597217268535228, \"text\": \"Chloe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our relationship worsened when I started setting boundaries.\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stood up for Chloe because I like her,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chloe, a Filipino-Australian who was raised in Australia, has her own income, he said.\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2663, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.7353203409386434, \"rank\": 0.3597217268535228, \"text\": \"Chloe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\"}, {\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9989764095583572, \"rank\": 0.0010058137874230353, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"First of all, Chloe has her own income.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.7353203409386434, \"rank\": 0.3597217268535228, \"text\": \"Chloe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything you see her using and all her travels come from her hard work,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mother judged Chloe right away because of how she dressed and acted.\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chloe and I grew up in different environments.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chloe grew up in Australia, and that's the culture she knows.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2996, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.7353203409386434, \"rank\": 0.3597217268535228, \"text\": \"Chloe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chloe_Sullivan\"}, {\"begin\": 3013, \"end\": 3022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9989764095583572, \"rank\": 0.0010058137874230353, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very different from how we move, talk, and dress in thePhilippines.\\\"\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": []}]}"